name: So.CUFFED.custom (PRE-ORDER)
description:
PRE-ORDER

NOTE: Please add what you are thinking of wanting on your cuff in the "NOTES FROM BUYER" section during checkout. I will follow up via e-mail and discuss what you want on your cuff and finalize it to a personalized and precious piece! Can't think of anything? No problem...that's where I come in! I love coming up with creative and new design ideas :)

Below are samples of different cuffs made. Follow on Instagram or head to my facebook page to see more examples and customized options.


Want to customize a cuff with a favorite Bible verse, word, saying, initial, or date? These are AMAZING gift ideas for a friend, mom, sister, the Bride to be, or bridesmaids!

Brass or Nickel cuff.

Each cuff has a slight bend to it, to adjust to your wist size. Brass and Nickel are a metals, which will tarnish and darken with your natural skin oils. It is important to take care of your metal by not wearing it in the shower, throwing lotion all over it, and to polish it up whenever you get the chance. Personally, I love when it darkens, for a more vintage look! You may use a polish pad or cloth to shine it back up.

Flower texture tool, streak textured hammer, and round ball hammer textures available. 

Stamps available: Heart, Anchor, or a Cross.

name: So.TAKEheart.bracelet
description:
TAKE HEART -Jesus. 

 "Take Heart" ...words of Jesus. It means: to be encouraged, cheer up, have hope, and be confident in His authority in your life. 

THIS FITS AROUND A 7 INCH WRIST (for a fitted and nice fit!)

Some inspiration from my Bible Study lately, as I study the whole book of Matthew with Bible Study Fellowship this year! This is also inspired by my old So.CHARMING style bracelets, but revamped.

This wraps around your wrist twice, with the tan suede cording. I stamped a LARGE sterling silver tag with TAKE HEART on it. I attached an antique brass spike and a how-lite cross charm on it. You attach the clasp to the end of the tag. This wrap gives it a layered look, but a simple statement maker. The clasp/hook is sterling silver as well.

name: So.JOHN15:5
description:
"I am the vine; you are the branches. If you remain in Me and I in you, you will bear much fruit; apart from Me you can do nothing." 
-John 15:5

I love this verse so much. It basically says it in a nutshell of who we are and Who God is. Without the vine, there would be no branches! Apart from HIM, we are nothing. I thought it would be cool to do a simple, yet statement necklace with a meaning behind it. 

Style: It will be shorter, collarbone length. The chain is hooked from one side of the branch to the other (same style as the sideways cross. This is a connector piece.) The branch will lay vertically (exactly like my tag necklaces.) This is a SHORTER necklace, so you can add longer strands of necklaces to dress it up. Wear it with t-shirt, or for a night out with a fun dress, to add a touch of class.

Materials: Sterling Silver branch and delicate chain option 14 kt gold filled delicate chain and 24kt gold VERMEIL branch. Choose your option under order options.

name: "Child of God" Tee (DISTRESSED)
description:
Cut up & distressed! I love to personalize and cut up tee's.....so I made this one a little more So.ME! It's a perfect summer tee, yet something fashionable with a pop of blue. I cut softer look into the neckline, and cut the sleeves and the bottom for a vintage look. Once washed, it will have more of a distressed and tattered look-LOVE mine. I put some holes in some areas on mine...if you want these or don't want them on yours...let me know in the NOTES SECTION!

"How great is the love, the Father has lavished on us; that we should be called, CHILDREN OF GOD, & that is what we are!" -1 John 3:1

So, I recently spent 2 months in India (January-March)...for mission work. It gave me a LOT of inspiration....from a Biblical standpoint & reflecting on my own walk with the Lord, as well as the people, colors, & culture. Head to the BLOG section and read about my time there! My friend and I spoke to thousands of kids, traveling to different cities and going into schools. We spoke to them about an identity that will never change; our identity in God. 

You may have the coolest job, be a billionaire, be the most popular chick, or star athlete....but think about it, that identity and label you have that people give you, will change over time & it doesn't last. Often times we seek to find our identity in other people, things, jobs, status, wealth (the list goes on & it is different for us all) to fully satisfy us. An identity that WILL last forever & is eternal, whether you are 5 or 80 years old...is our Identity in God. God views & VALUES you as one of His CHILDREN. Our identity and security must be found in Him! 

Will you rep one of these? 1 John 3:1 

SIZE CHART IS THE LAST PHOTO ON THIS LISTING. 

Bella Unisex Jersey (thinner material) Tee in ROYAL BLUE! This is a unisex fit...meaning it is a slouchy, oversized fit. Order a size smaller for a more fitted look. Very comfy!

100% combed ring-spun cotton, 4.2 oz., 142 gm/m² super soft 30 single baby jersey knit.

name: So.JACQUELINE
description:
This cuff bracelet is a dark brown dyed tooling leather. The supplier who supplied me with this awesome leather to work with, is Tafuri Tough™ Design Studios. I added my own personal touch with the rivets to the plain leather bracelets.

This is a single wrap snap cuff bracelet. It's size is an average fit when snapped with both of the snaps provided. It is roughly around 6 inches in the inner diameter of the bracelet when it's snapped on BOTH snaps. If you snapped it on the outer snap only, it would give you a little more room. THIS IS FOR A PETITE WRIST. My wrist is about 6 inches round, and this is snug on my wrist. It fits, but I'd rather do the next size up. This is intended for petite sized wrists!

It is a tougher and firmer leather, but once you wear it in a bit, it will soften and become more flexible.

I used brass pyramid rivets & then punched holes in it in a few areas to give it some character and detail. This is unique & one of a kind. It looks great if you layered it with a few other bracelets you may have!

ATTN: This leather is NOT waterproof. It softens as you wear it. The snaps are heavy duty & lead free. All leather cuffs were provided by Tafuri Tough™ Design Studios. I, myself, personalized and added rivets and detail to the plain leather pieces they provided me.
